data.description: Immaculate historic two story 1 Family home with a grand finished basement in the Far Rockaway section of Queens. 4 Bedrooms 2.5 Baths. Home sitting on a 54.05' X 125' IRR lot size. 1 Car garage with a long drive that fits up to 4 cars or more. As you enter the grand entrance you have a beautiful front porch with ample space. As you enter the home you'll notice the high ceilings, gorgeous exposed beams throughout, beautiful natural hardwood floors throughout, open flow with the spacious living room & large formal dining room, gas fire place, study room/office right off the living room, half bath, spacious kitchen with a breakfast nook. 2nd level offers 4 spacious bedrooms with great closet spacious, luxurious full bath with a elegant claw foot tub and standup shower. Home is drenched in natural sun light, full finished basement, grand backyard with phenomenal space for gardening and entertaining. The home is in pristine condition. Conveniently located steps away from the #A Subway station, multiple bus lines, near schools, public transportation, parks, major highways, hospitals and shopping hubs.
